					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Amusingly, the handle @jun_fappist that I’ve used for fun online still lives through this endeavor.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"好玩的是，因为嗜好而使用的名字“@junonanist”还活得好好的。",
