					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"She hasn’t done much fighting since graduating from Minotsuki Academy. She’s also lost the title of drill sergeant from hell and is now known internally as everyone’s friendly older sister.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"水乃月学园毕业以后就没再实战了，原本的魔鬼教官样也变成了温柔可人的SHO姐姐风。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"水乃月學園畢業以後就沒再實戰了，原本的魔鬼教官樣也變成了溫柔可人的SHO姊姊風。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
